Almost Half of Germans Oppose Aid for Greece, Welt Reports

-- B y   A a r o n   K i r c h f e l d
-- 
2011-05-08T11:50:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-08/almost-half-of-germans-oppose-aid-for-greece-welt-reports.html
Forty-seven percent of Germans are
opposed to providing financial aid to  Greece , Welt am Sonntag
reported, citing a  survey  conducted by GfK SE.  Only 20 percent of those surveyed support helping the
government in  Athens , the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Aaron Kirchfeld in Frankfurt at 
